description:
Danny breaks down this year's Vanderpump Rules Pride episode, which features Scheana and Katie doing arts & crafts, colorful costumes, the return of James and Raquel, and much more! Danny also discusses QIL Renée Zellweger's Oscar acceptance speech, which is likely still going on.
